OL,3,CDog walker's wife may have heard him
OL,4,Ccalling to her before dying in Storm
OL,5,CBert
OL,7,FThe wife of a retired teacher who died
OL,8,Fin the flooded River Conwy during
OL,9,FStorm Bert may have heard him calling
OL,10,Fto her, an inquest has heard.
OL,12,FA major search was launched when 75-
OL,13,Fyear-old Brian Perry was reported
OL,14,Fmissing after taking his Collie dog
OL,15,Ffor a walk at the village of Trefriw,
OL,16,Fnear Llanrwst, during Storm Bert on
OL,17,FNovember 23.
