OL,3,CDog walker's wife may have heard him
OL,4,Ccalling to her before dying in Storm
OL,5,CBert
OL,7,F"She said she may have heard him
OL,8,Fshouting," the coroner said.
OL,10,FCoastguards, police, the fire and
OL,11,Frescue service, and Ogwen Valley
OL,12,Fmountain rescue team volunteers
OL,13,Fscoured the area until 9pm and then
OL,14,Fresumed the search the following
OL,15,Fmorning.
OL,17,FMr Perry's body was found later that
OL,18,Fday on 24 November by the police
OL,19,Funderwater search team in Gower Road,
OL,20,FTrefriw, where the water had been
OL,21,Fchest-high.
